TeleGraph: Graph of citations of channels about ML / DS / AI

What's that?
  • Each node is a telegram channel
  • Arrows A → B indicates that channel A cited channel B
  • Node size is the number of citations
  • Channels are arranged according to their similarity
How does it work?
  • Use the mouse to zoom and move
  • Hover over a channel to see information about it
  • Click on a channel to see its connections
  • Use the filters at the top to search
Author: @ai_about_ai
